      "value": "<p>You take in a big breath and cross your arms in an X pattern and then unleash a mighty scream that reaches even the heavens. You make 3 60-foot cones that spread out in different directions. The cones cannot overlap. Each creature in one of the cones must make a Dexterity saving throw taking 10d12+10 fire damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>",
